                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> The prisoner's Employ who only to bind the hay—he sold ten loads at Blackheath—he had not the least authority to tell any—he could not imagine that he had—I never mentioned the price of it to him—I think I told him I had sold Smith some at 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I did not tell him I wished to sell the rest if he had brought me the money I should have reprimanded him for selling it.</p>
